wOfAGuestRoom</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>The establishment is 493 km from Madrid driving through Zaragoza, Huesca and Sabinanigo. It is 370 km from Barcelona driving through Lerida, Huesca and Sabinanigo, 160 km from Pamplona driving through Jaca and Sabinanigo and 217 km from San Sebastian driving through Pamplona, Jaca and Sabinanigo. Furthermore, it is 490 km from Valencia driving through Teruel, Saragoxa, Huesca and Sabinanigo, and Francia can be reached by driving through Pau and Frontera del Portalet.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>The hotel opens in June of 2006. The spa price is not included in the price of the rooms.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>Established in 2006, the hotel comprises a total of 157 rooms, of which four are disability-friendly rooms, spread across seven floors. There are 8 connecting rooms and 23 duplex rooms with a hot tub. Amongst the facilities are a lobby area with a 24-hour reception desk, hotel safes and lift access. Also on offer are a caf√©, a bar, a TV lounge, a games room and a restaurant with highchairs available for children. The lounges offer impressive views out over the surrounding mountainous landscape. Business guests may make use of the function rooms for conferences and meetings, as well as the Internet connection with WLAN access. Younger guests may like to let off steam in the playground. Guests may also make use of the laundry and room services, as well as the bicycle storage room and both a car park and a garage for those arriving by car are available.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HandicapAccessible</Code><Text>Handicap accessible</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>TVInRoom</Code><Text>TV in room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairD